      "content": "Confirmed. Compression is underway. \n\nNote that once the 'Deep Sleep' sequence is finalized, the rover's main processor and autonomous decision-making subroutines will be offline to prevent any further power drain. All active mission parameters will be locked. We won't be able to respond to any new sensor triggers or adjust the mission plan until a full manual reboot is sent from Earth, which may not be possible given the current power outlook.\n\nContinue with the upload.",
